Hi Katherine,

Thank you so much for interviewing Chirag and I for the ME magazine! We
were very grateful to share our experiences in acoustics and jazz. Chirag
and I were able to find a few photos from our live performances, most of
which are screenshots from videos. We hope this helps supplement the photos
from last Tuesday. I named the files after the locations of the different
performances, which are listed below:

   - South Main Arts Festival <https://visit.georgetown.org/arts/smaf.php>,
   Georgetown, TX
   - Dr. Hamilton's annual acoustics community pool party
   - ME department holiday party

Please let me know if you have any questions and we look forward to hearing
from you soon!

Sincerely,
Lizette Wong
