 live performances, most of which are
 screenshots from videos. We hope this helps supplement the photos from las=
t Tuesday. I named the files after the locations of the different performan=
ces, which are listed=C2=A0below:</div>
<ul style=3D"direction:ltr">
<li style=3D"direction:ltr"><a href=3D"https://visit.georgetown.org/arts/sm=
af.php" target=3D"_blank">South Main Arts Festival</a>, Georgetown, TX</li>=
<li style=3D"direction:ltr">Dr. Hamilton&#39;s annual acoustics community p=
ool party</li><li style=3D"direction:ltr">ME department holiday party</li><=
/ul>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr">Please let me know if you have any questions a=
nd we look forward to hearing from you soon!</div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr"><br>
</div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr">Sincerely,</div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr">Lizette Wong</div>
